{"tid":2087853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安法通過前夕 中國釋放被扣押前美軍機師","createTime":"2020-07-01T00:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T01:07:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca9b746abae8a87a5016775c41af1d19a5a8e04","tid":2087853,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"中國在通過香港「國安法」前夕，釋放去年9月在廣東被扣查的聯邦快遞（FedEx）美籍機師翰恩（Todd A. Hohn）。翰恩目前已離開中國，與家人團聚，他透過律師表示，不會因此敵視中國，又稱期望未來再臨中國。<br />\n<br />\n翰恩來自佛羅里達州，為美國退役空軍機師，官至上校，2017年加入聯邦快遞，及後搬到香港。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n翰恩代表律師賽門（Theodore Simon）表示，翰恩其後獲准保釋外出，但不准離開中國。經過9個月調查和司法程序後，翰恩最終獲宣告無罪，在6月27日離開中國，與家人團聚，<span style=\"color: red;\">「雖然翰恩經歷了這些苦難，但他表示（中國）當局有禮和尊重他，他對中國、中國政府及中國人民，都不存敵意，期望有一天回到那裡（中國）。」 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得留意是，翰恩去年被捕時，正值香港「反送中」抗爭運動白熱化之際，最終於北京強行在香港實行「國安法」前獲釋；期間，美中關係因貿易戰、武漢肺炎疫情蔓延全球、北京加強打壓香港等原因，日漸惡化。 <br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200701/OR2CMVFDAS6742W5R3ZOYASV6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200701%2FOR2CMVFDAS6742W5R3ZOYASV6M%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=8ee8e9de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200701%2FOR2CMVFDAS6742W5R3ZOYASV6M%2F&h=62bdae38\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200701/OR2CMVFDAS6742W5R3ZOYASV6M/</a>"},{"pid":"b8cb4bcbcbdbe0e2658cc59efca6256e45d7f2a2","tid":2087853,"uid":67353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"坐戰鬥返中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611274214f4f199a20a4a1387b9aa276fd117c18","tid":2087853,"uid":67353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8cb4bcbcbdbe0e2658cc59efca6256e45d7f2a2","tid":2087853,"uid":67353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"坐戰鬥返中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:43:51.000Z","msg":"戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99676cf6d9e4600325aff2589dc07cca4b32aa5","tid":2087853,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:44:42.000Z","msg":"Spy"},{"pid":"16622a8841a7446b57acffe11a22e7fe6e06db94","tid":2087853,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:45:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲人應該要死刑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ddd62485357b4a4d3757bd8565e66e52106deb","tid":2087853,"uid":278298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"所以點解咁多人想做美國人。<br />\n你睇吓加拿大人?"},{"pid":"e5eb5562969a4e17560cd7571537b648341328b8","tid":2087853,"uid":77731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:46:17.000Z","msg":"不存敵意<br />\n係非常有中國色彩既說話<br />\n詳情參考國安法"},{"pid":"f8267555c5796cd091cbc7fc464a8f4752f06099"